      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHO'S IN DEV (6) is a leader who scored heavily bet in Maidens two back before a 1.5L defeat this track/trip as a $4.2 favourite. Keeps improving and has weight relief. Will control the race and rates to bounce back. THEM'S THE BREAKS (9) is busting to win and has been cruelled by wide barriers. Came hard to just miss this track/trip last time as a $3.6 favourite and finally has an inside barrier. Can fight out the finish if things go her way. ILOVETHISTOWN (4) will present at peak fitness and has been within range over 1200m since his easy Maiden win at the track, backed off the map. Raced favourite last time and has been kept up to the mark with a Longford trial win. Has an awkward gate but keeps the top hoop and will push forward and give a big sight. WOOLCLASSER (3) and WINDARA WOLF (2) both present third-up off comfortable Maiden wins and have more to offer.",
